'''Domain Lacap''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War|Yuuzhan Vong invasion]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], Domain Lacap was granted stewardship of a whole star system by [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]]. However, when [[Warmaster]] [[Nas Choka]] ordered them to [[Coruscant/Legends|Yuuzhan'tar]] to aid his armada in destroying [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]], Domain Lacap refused to send a single ship.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

